{"tid":1688361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"華盛頓與毛澤東曾經處於劣勢，但最終獲得勝利。香港人既堅持亦都可以。","createTime":"2019-11-02T11:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T12:54:28.000Z","uid":251265,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e75a245691a4f1416ab6ea9196f595dee7016e84","tid":1688361,"uid":251265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:37:37.000Z","msg":"毛澤東堅持左３０年，最終打贏國民黨，而華盛頓亦堅持左１０年，最後逐出英軍<br />\n縱使兩件歷史事件無論導火線或者爭取手法都不一樣，<br />\n但係佢地既手足都堅持自己既信念到最後勝利，<br />\n最後希望香港人無論處於點樣既劣勢都唔好放棄，亦都唔好亂比POPO帶風向。<br />\n香港人反抗！"},{"pid":"2ef3874e4a012d80551a3f00188f8044371cb1eb","tid":1688361,"uid":251265,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:40:29.000Z","msg":"係港島返到黎之後見到好多放棄ＰＯＳＴ，要加油呀唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4968d991b518753194f04eb6fba395967341090","tid":1688361,"uid":193233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:42:22.000Z","msg":"呢樣真，每次遊行聚會都吹失敗風！"},{"pid":"6db5ac7cf2ec3a758ae0889b25181999ebf81043","tid":1688361,"uid":121562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:43:12.000Z","msg":"荷蘭捱左80年"},{"pid":"4fb9d2580775a566b3baebec7e7d5ecefa3cc5db","tid":1688361,"uid":61282,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"睇老毛嘅《論持久戰》就知佢當年都面對好多失敗主義撚，同end game撚，但佢明確指出無論係失敗撚定end game撚都是不對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097ea0b3f7a459e21e556861f012ed13074418ca","tid":1688361,"uid":170445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:43:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a92f37aafcdd37f3b856128cea50f97fbb06c6a6","tid":1688361,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4fb9d2580775a566b3baebec7e7d5ecefa3cc5db","tid":168836